node.text:
🎧 ⬆️ I’m breaking down @myopenfit 4 Weeks of Focus program for you + I have a feeling you’re about to start working out with me.  

I know as much as anyone that getting a fitness routine started is the hardest part, so we are stripping down the excuses so we can "snap forward” together.

👉🏻 I'm releasing the first 2 days of the workout FREE on my Youtube channel. 
👉🏻 If you start within the week you’ll get 75% off with an annual plan
🥳 that is less that $5 a month

openfit.com/4WOF

node.text: When the 🌕 hits your 👀 like a big…..tortilla pizza? I mean that isn’t quite right, but this pizza definitely is.  Tune in to today’s Shay’s Kitchen to learn how to make a very fast and delicious….”pizza,” and the Tik Tok sensation that is the Oreo Mug Cake. Should I be concerned that a cookie basically turns into a cake? Yes I should be. Do I care? No.

node.text:
For Cinco de Mayo this year, @chadwoodhair and I wanted to learn more...well, about Cinco de Mayo. Let’s just say the surprise was on us (but mostly him💁🏻‍♀️!)

In this special edition of the Chad and Shay #shitshow we explore some of our favorite Mexican-inspired cocktails and mocktails.

🎶: @mariachi_teocuitatlan

node.text: You think you know someone, but have you ever spent an afternoon at their own personal sanctuary? I mean I have obviously spent time at the pad of @chadwoodinteriors but you may not have. Let’s change that.  From flea market finds to flowers cut (read: stolen) from his neighbor's yard, check out today’s video to see where this eclectic Chad of All Trades spends his downtime.
Béis CAMP 🌲/ launching Sept 22 @ 9am!!! Second slide: how we got the shot! 🤣
